      "remarks": "OSCAL profile expressing the Salesforce Baseline Standard (SBS) as a platform-specific sub-profile of SSCF v1.0. Selects all SSCF controls applicable to Salesforce CRM/Platform deployments. Controls requiring manual verification (DSP-004 cross-border, DSP-006 privacy rights, IPY-004 exit planning) are included as manual-assessment controls. This profile is the control basis for the salesforce_component.json component definition.",
